   Marketing &amp; Media:
   More Brand Names
   Gain Recognition
   Around the World
   ---
   Survey Finds Top 20 Products
   In Terms of Awareness,
   Esteem From Consumers
   ----
   By Kathleen Deveny
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/13/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B7
</SO>
